ents\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aqo1665702655995.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aqo1665702655995.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aqo1665702655995\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /sym\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether object references are generated during compilation, and where they are located.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__section_w2933ab1b5b1_w2934ab1b5_w2935ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__p_d151382e1_d151383e1_d151384e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/sym</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__section_w2936ab1b5b3_w2937ab1b5_w2938ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d190715e76\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title draft-comment\">Arguments</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__2\">Do not store object references during\n\t\t\t\t\t compilation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__2\">Store object references in symbol table\n\t\t\t\t\t files in the working directory</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__1\">2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__2\">Generate cross-reference data to the\n\t\t\t\t\t UXCROSS repository table from internal object references</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__1\">3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqo1665702655995__table_d18284e1_d18285e1_d18286e1__entry__2\">Store object references to symbol table\n\t\t\t\t\t files and generate cross-reference data in the UXCROSS repository table</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__section_w2939ab1b5b5_w2940ab1b5_w2941ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d190715e146\">\n                  \n Use with\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52655e1_d52656e1_d52657e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52658e1_d52659e1_d52660e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52661e1_d52662e1_d52663e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifp1665702626096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702626096.html\" title=\"Compile all components, including server pages, HTML forms, forms, reports, services, entity services, and session services.\">/cpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52664e1_d52665e1_d52666e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52667e1_d52668e1_d52669e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1665702626915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1665702626915.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface entity service components.\">/esv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52670e1_d52671e1_d52672e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52673e1_d52674e1_d52675e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixo1665702655853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixo1665702655853.html\" title=\"Compile global ProcScript and variables in a library.\">/lib</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52676e1_d52677e1_d52678e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxo1665702656136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxo1665702656136.html\" title=\"Compile menu bars, menus, and menu items.\">/men</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52679e1_d52680e1_d52681e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tku1665702656275.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tku1665702656275.html\" title=\"Compile global objects.\">/obj</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52682e1_d52683e1_d52684e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kwp1719764280859.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kwp1719764280859.html\" title=\"Compile panels.\">/pan</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52685e1_d52686e1_d52687e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52688e1_d52689e1_d52690e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"umc1665702653094.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umc1665702653094.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface session service components.\">/ssv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__li_d52691e1_d52692e1_d52693e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__section_w2942ab1b5b7_w2943ab1b5_w2944ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d190715e287\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aqo1665702655995__p_d151394e1_d151395e1_d151396e1\">Use this switch to override the value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SYMBOL_TABLE</span> assignment setting.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpw1665702656511.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$SYMBOL_TABLE</a><p>Specifies whether symbol table files and cross-reference data are generated during compilation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525834\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525834\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/sym Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /sym Specify whether object references are generated during compilation, and where they are located. /sym = 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 Parameters Table 1. Arguments Value Meaning 0 Do not store object references during compilation 1 Store object references in symbol table files in the working directory 2 Generate cross-reference data to the UXCROSS repository table from internal object references 3 Store object references to symbol table files and generate cross-reference data in the UXCROSS repository table Use with /all /aps or /app /cpt /dsp /esv /frm /lib /men /obj /pan /rpt /ssv /usp Description Use this switch to override the value of the $SYMBOL_TABLE assignment setting. Related Links $SYMBOL_TABLE Specifies whether symbol table files and cross-reference data are generated during compilation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}